{"prompt": "Generate a website for a SaaS product. The website should be lively and use red as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>SaaS Product</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-color: #E53935; /* A lively red */\n            --secondary-color: #FCE4EC; /* A very light pink, a subtle contrast */\n            --text-color: #212121;\n            --light-text-color: #FFFFFF;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--secondary-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            overflow-x: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-color) 0%, #EF5350 100%);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 3.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.3em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            max-width: 700px;\n            margin-left: auto;\n            margin-right: auto;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            display: inline-block;\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n            border: 2px solid var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-3px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n        }\n\n        .features {\n            padding: 80px 20px;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .features h2 {\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 40px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            max-width: 1000px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item {\n            background-color: var(--light-text-color);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item i {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .feature-item h3 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            color: var(--brand-color);\n        }\n\n        .feature-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-color);\n            color: var(--light-text-color);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 40px 20px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 1em;\n        }\n\n        /* Simple animation for a lively feel */\n        @keyframes fadeInUp {\n            from {\n                opacity: 0;\n                transform: translateY(20px);\n            }\n            to {\n                opacity: 1;\n                transform: translateY(0);\n            }\n        }\n\n        .hero, .features h2, .feature-item {\n            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards;\n        }\n        .hero h1 { animation-delay: 0.2s; }\n        .hero p { animation-delay: 0.4s; }\n        .cta-button { animation-delay: 0.6s; }\n        .features h2 { animation-delay: 0.8s; }\n        .feature-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 1.0s; }\n        .feature-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 1.2s; }\n        .feature-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 1.4s; }\n\n    </style>\n    <!-- Font Awesome for icons -->\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Revolutionize Your Workflow</h1>\n        <p>Our cutting-edge SaaS solution empowers your team to achieve more, faster. Experience seamless collaboration and unparalleled efficiency.</p>\n        <a href=\"#features\" class=\"cta-button\">Learn More</a>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"features\" id=\"features\">\n        <h2>Key Features</h2>\n        <div class=\"feature-grid\">\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-rocket\"></i>\n                <h3>Blazing Fast Performance</h3>\n                <p>Engineered for speed, our platform ensures you never miss a beat, delivering results in real-time.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-shield-alt\"></i>\n                <h3>Rock-Solid Security</h3>\n                <p>Your data is our priority. We employ state-of-the-art security measures to keep your information safe.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"feature-item\">\n                <i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i>\n                <h3>Effortless Collaboration</h3>\n                <p>Bring your team together with intuitive tools designed for seamless communication and project management.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Your SaaS Product. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}